<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>To the question of Fornost on the BF Helm, you need to kill Corflunk and Zarchoomie in Butcherblock mountains, they tend to roam around. Take both their heads to Byzil Bloodforge and he rewards you with RANDOM pieces of BF armor. If you are lucky, and the wind blows in the right direction, you will get the BF helm. If not, keep hunting (not camping) the two ogres known as Corflunk and Zarchoomie. Take a ranger!<BR>
<BR>
Drakklon of Vallon Zek. (I got me 2 of these babies, the first I sold, and the second was a gift to a close friend, Branwyn)</font></td></tr></table>
